<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Challenge1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Challenge,</orth> subst. 1) claim: <cit><quote>of benefit proceeding from our king, and not of any c. of desert,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.4.153" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 4, 153</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) an exception made in law against a person: <cit><quote>and make my c. you shall not be my judge,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 2.4.77" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 4, 77</bibl></cit> (but perhaps here also == claim).
<lb />3) summons to single combat: <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.4.114" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 4, 114</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 1.1.41" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado I, 1, 41</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 5.1.145" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 145</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 5.2.57" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 57</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.713" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 713</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 2.3.140" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. II, 3, 140</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 3.2.43" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 43</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 3.4.157" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 4, 157</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 3.4.157" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 4, 157</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.2.53" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A V, 2, 53</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 1.3.272" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 3, 272</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 3.3.35" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 35</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 2.4.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. II, 4, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 4.6.141" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 6, 141</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 4.1.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. IV, 1, 6</bibl>.
